params.description: Output only. The full, unique name of this Membership resource in the format projects/*/locations/*/memberships/{membership_id}, set during creation. membership_id must be a valid RFC 1123 compliant DNS label: 1. At most 63 characters in length 2. It must consist of lower case alphanumeric characters or - 3.
